##############################################################
#
#  Setup
#
#

Context("Numeric");
#given
$W= random(500,1000,10);# [N]

#computation
$Ans =sqrt($W/(998*pi/4*(0.05)**2));# [m/s]

#set tolerance
Context()->flags->set(
tolerance=>.05,);

##############################################################
#
#  PGML 
#
#

BEGIN_PGML

[@ image("UBC-FLU-18-065.png", width=>[$width], height=>[$height]) @]*

In the figure a perfectly balanced [`[$W]`] [`N`] weight and platform are supported by a steady water jet.  What is the jet's velocity if the platform's mass is negligible?

[`v=`] [____]{"$Ans"} [`m/s`]

END_PGML

